改革：
Reform and opening up have greatly stimulated people's enthusiasm.
改革开放极大的激发了人们的积极性
The people already are largely motivated and the productivity has been greatly improved.
人民已经得到了很大的积极性，生产力也得到了很大的提高。
One aim of these reforms is effective defence with minimal expenditure. 
这些改革的目的之一是以最低成本实现有效防御。
The Government wants to accelerate the pace of structural reforms.
政府想要加快结构改革的步伐。
The government has initiated a series of reforms. 
政府开始实施了一系列改革。
Some is cynical about reform.
有些人对改革持悲观态度。
the incessant demand for change came from leading politicians that characterizes our time 
对变革的不断要求来自于我们这个时代的主要的政治家

